PN,31801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772817082
OL,3,CFirst UK government flight due to
OL,4,Cbring citizens home from Middle East
OL,5,Cdelayed
OL,7,FThe first flight organised by UK
OL,8,Fgovernment to bring British nationals
OL,9,Fhome from the Middle East has been
OL,10,Fdelayed due to a "technical issue".
OL,12,FThe government-chartered flight
OL,13,Fcarrying Britons left stranded in the
OL,14,Fregion after the outbreak of the US-
OL,15,FIsraeli war on Iran was expected to
OL,16,Fland in the UK early on Thursday.
OL,18,FBut the flight from, Muscat, the
OL,19,Fcapital of Oman, failed to depart as
OL,20,Fplanned due to what the Foreign Office
OL,21,Fconfirmed to be "technical issues".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772817082
OL,3,CFirst UK government flight due to
OL,4,Cbring citizens home from Middle East
OL,5,Cdelayed
OL,7,F"The flight is now expected to depart
OL,8,Flater today," the government
OL,9,Fdepartment added.
OL,11,FIt comes after the US and Israel
OL,12,Fintensified their bombing attacks
OL,13,Fagainst Iran's military and security
OL,14,Fapparatus as the conflict entered its
OL,15,Fsixth day on Thursday.
OL,17,FMuscat, which is some 300 miles by
OL,18,Froad from Dubai and Abu Dhabi, has
OL,19,Femerged as a key location for people
OL,20,Fto leave the Middle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
