PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772817082
OL,3,CFirst UK government flight due to
OL,4,Cbring citizens home from Middle East
OL,5,Cdelayed
OL,7,FThis is because the vast majority of
OL,8,Fcommercial flights from the United
OL,9,FArab Emirates are cancelled due to
OL,10,Fairspace restrictions caused by the
OL,11,Fconflict.
OL,13,FPrime minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,14,Fannounced two further government-
OL,15,Fchartered flights, one of which is
OL,16,Fexpected to leave Oman on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
