PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772817082
OL,3,CFirst UK government flight due to
OL,4,Cbring citizens home from Middle East
OL,5,Cdelayed
OL,7,FTwo more commercial British Airways
OL,8,Fflights are due to take passengers
OL,9,Ffrom Muscat to London Heathrow on
OL,10,FFriday and Saturday. Some 138,000
OL,11,FBritish nationals have registered
OL,12,Ftheir presence in the Middle East.
OL,14,FQatar Airways announced it would
OL,15,Foperate "a limited number of relief
OL,16,Fflights" to European cities on
OL,17,FThursday, but confirmed most flights
OL,18,Fwould remain suspended due to the
OL,19,Fongoing closure of Qatari airspace.
OL,26,@wD@IOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
