CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772817082
OL,3,CFirst UK government flight due to
OL,4,Cbring citizens home from Middle East
OL,5,Cdelayed
OL,7,FServices from Muscat would depart for
OL,8,FLondon Heathrow as well as Madrid,
OL,9,FRome, Amsterdam and Copenhagen.
OL,10,FAnother flight would depart from Saudi
OL,11,FArabia's capital city, Riyadh, to
OL,12,FFrankfurt.
OL,14,F"Passengers are kindly requested not
OL,15,Fto proceed to the airport unless they
OL,16,Fhave received an official notification
OL,17,Ffrom Qatar Airways for these flights,"
OL,18,Fthe airline wrote in a statement on X.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@fO]
