OL,3,CFirst UK government flight due to
OL,4,Cbring citizens home from Middle East
OL,5,Cdelayed
OL,7,FA limited number of commercial flights
OL,8,Fhave been leaving the UAE, with more
OL,9,Fthan 300 people returning to Scotland
OL,10,Ffrom Dubai via the Emirates airline on
OL,11,FWednesday night.
OL,13,FFamilies broke down in tears of relief
OL,14,Fas they embraced their loved ones, who
OL,15,Ftouched down at Edinburgh Airport at
OL,16,F8.12pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
