OL,3,CFirst UK government flight due to
OL,4,Cbring citizens home from Middle East
OL,5,Cdelayed
OL,7,FVictoria Cameron, 57, originally from
OL,8,FSouth Africa but now residing in
OL,9,FLarkhall, is partially deaf, and was
OL,10,Fmet with a bunch of flowers from her
OL,11,Fhusband, Brian Cameron.
OL,13,FRemembering the initial missile
OL,14,Fattacks on Saturday, she said: "I
OL,15,Fthought it was a firework. Then we saw
OL,16,Fthe second one, then the third one and
OL,17,Fwe started screaming and the hotel
OL,18,Fstaff said 'run, run, run'.
OL,26,@vD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
