PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772817082
OL,3,CFirst UK government flight due to
OL,4,Cbring citizens home from Middle East
OL,5,Cdelayed
OL,7,F"I was on the phone to my husband,
OL,8,Fsaying 'we're under fire' and they led
OL,9,Fus away, the phones were going, we
OL,10,Fwere shaking and we were crying.
OL,12,F"I'm from South Africa, and I'm not
OL,13,Fscared of anything, we're used to
OL,14,Fstuff, but I thought I was a goner on
OL,15,FSaturday night."
OL,17,FMr Cameron, 59, had intended to travel
OL,18,Fto Dubai by any means necessary after
OL,19,Fhearing his wife might be in danger.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
