OL,3,CFirst UK government flight due to
OL,4,Cbring citizens home from Middle East
OL,5,Cdelayed
OL,7,F"I'd come up with all sorts of plans
OL,8,Fto drive there, just to be with her, I
OL,9,Fdidn't like her being on her own," he
OL,10,Fsaid. "The relief is just... I can't
OL,11,Fput it into words."
OL,13,FJack Crowe, 26, owner of Borders
OL,14,FCompetitions, remembered hearing the
OL,15,Ffirst explosions on Saturday.
OL,17,FHe said: "I think when it first hit
OL,18,Ffor me was, we were on The Palm, and
OL,19,Four balcony looked inland, and a jet
OL,20,Fflew over.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@bO]rD@GOUsD@SO]yD@JOU
