OL,7,F"I ran out to film it and was
OL,8,Ffollowing the jet, and then there was
OL,9,Fthis massive explosion. I was like,
OL,10,F'what the hell was that?'"
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FHoliday-goers Fiona Shearer, 45, and
OL,18,FLynn Buttercase, 49, described feeling
OL,19,F"on edge" during the initial strikes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@ZO]{D@AOU{D@IO]
