OL,3,CFirst UK government flight due to
OL,4,Cbring citizens home from Middle East
OL,5,Cdelayed
OL,7,FMs Shearer said: "The Saturday was
OL,8,Fobviously horrendous. We were all
OL,9,Freally on edge, because you could
OL,10,Fstill hear the explosions in the sky
OL,11,Fand things. We heard the airport
OL,12,Fexplosion, and then these phone alerts
OL,13,Fwent off."
OL,15,FMs Buttercase said: "In the basement
OL,16,Fof our hotel they made bunkers in
OL,17,Funderground garages, so everyone slept
OL,18,Fwith their clothes on with their grab-
OL,19,Fbag, passport and had our phones fully
OL,20,Fcharged."
